```{r pancreas 32948965, include=FALSE}

PMID_32948965 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32948965', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32948965 <- paste0(PMID_32948965$journal,' ', PMID_32948965$year, ' ', PMID_32948965$month,';', PMID_32948965$volume,'(', PMID_32948965$number,'):', PMID_32948965$pages)

PubMed_32948965 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32948965$eprint)

doi_32948965 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32948965$doi)
```
